$interpreted: Gang Member: Boss, Dylan is coming after us!

Gang Leader: Dylan Levon! What did we do to ruffle his feathers!?
Whatever, grab the valuables and let's get our butts outta here!
Jahan: Whew~ Sir Dylan, I've come to help.
Dylan: The leader got away; come with me. We'll chase him down!
Jahan: S...So exhausting...we've pretty much taken care of every single gang in the capital for the past half a month.
Jahan: Just what in the world is Dylan doing...but thank goodness...
Dylan: I said come with me!
Dylan: This is...
Jahan: D-Did we get him? I was just a teeny-bit late, or I could've helped Sir Dylan.
Jahan: Whew, let me take a quick breath...
Dylan: Jahan, take him and his subordinates back.
Jahan: What? But he's...
Dylan: He's badly injured and should not be able to move anytime soon. The incident with the assassin won't happen again.
Jahan: Yes Sir... then Sir Dylan, you...
Dylan: I still have other things to investigate. You take over from here.
Gang Leader: Hmm? I recognize you!
Gang Leader: Weren't you the dude who lost a ton of money to me at the Casino a while ago and had to pawn a golden cup in order to pay me?
Jahan: Shhhhhhhh! Shut up!
Gang Leader: So it's your fault that I'm getting screwed...ugh!
Jahan: Whew~ that was close, almost blew my cover...looks like I'll need an even better disguise the next time I get my hands dirty.
Jahan: As for this little fella, "death via brutal beating from Dylan"...sounds pretty good...
